<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
      .email-container {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
    max-width: 600px;
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    border: 2px solid #dddddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); 
}

.header {
    background-color: #F45F20;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-top-left-radius: 8px;
    border-top-right-radius: 8px;
}

.header h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 24px;
    text-align: center;
}

.content {
    padding: 20px;
}

.content p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.5;
}

.otp-code {
    display: block;
    margin: 20px 0;
    padding: 10px;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-align: center;
    color: #333;
    background-color: #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

.footer {
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    color: #777;
}

.footer p {
    margin: 5px 0;
}

    </style>
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>OTP Verification</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= userName %>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering with us. To complete your registration, please use the following OTP:</p>
            <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
            <p>This OTP is valid for the next 10 minutes. Please do not share this OTP with anyone.</p>
            <p>If you did not request this OTP, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>Vaanijyashala</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
